                        android:text="Condition 10/10. \nPerfect Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus suscipit lacus nec ante ullamcorper, non luctus neque fermentum. Donec quis elementum arcu. Aenean congue sapien ornare, scelerisque dolor pellentesque, porttitor risus."
